        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer436348850" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer7611978314685299907">In her debut novel, Melodie Ramone reaches out to readers and invites them to a lovely place in her heart. Her passion as a writer is reflected in this uplifting tale that begins with teenagers Sylvia, Oliver, and Alexander, and stretches into the golden years. The experiences that come with raising a family and having lifelong friendships run the gamut of emotions in the story, and in more than one instance, I found myself thinking, “I can relate to that!” Melodie Ramone’s writing style is cand</span>
  <span id="freeText7611978314685299907" style="display:none">In her debut novel, Melodie Ramone reaches out to readers and invites them to a lovely place in her heart. Her passion as a writer is reflected in this uplifting tale that begins with teenagers Sylvia, Oliver, and Alexander, and stretches into the golden years. The experiences that come with raising a family and having lifelong friendships run the gamut of emotions in the story, and in more than one instance, I found myself thinking, “I can relate to that!” Melodie Ramone’s writing style is candid, her characters are endearing, and her storyline is exceptional. After Forever Ends will stay with me for a long time. I highly recommend this book to anyone who wants to be taken to a special place.</span>
  <a data-text-id="7611978314685299907" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

