<li class='cover' id='bookCover_49047293'>
<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/49047293-enemies"><img alt="Enemies" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1575261187l/49047293._SX98_.jpg" />
